tip.text: Had a fantastic wine tasting here. Has a large stock of all types of wine and free tastings of some each week.

tip.text: Great tour from one of the family. Spent time understanding vines themselves and knowledgable host answered many questions from our small group. Very good wine at fantastic prices!
